OL,3,CThousands gather for summer solstice
OL,4,Cas UK braces for sweltering heatwave
OL,6,FThousands have gathered to celebrate
OL,7,Fthe summer solstice as the UK braces
OL,8,Fto bake in a heatwave that could see
OL,9,Frecord-breaking temperatures.
OL,11,FThe Met Office said the heat is
OL,12,Fexpected to peak at about 35C on
OL,13,FTuesday and Wednesday, sparking
OL,14,Fweather warnings, health alerts and
OL,15,Fconcerns for vulnerable people.
OL,17,FForecasters have said there is
OL,18,F"growing confidence" this week could
OL,19,Fbreak the record for the hottest June
OL,20,Ftemperature of 35.6C, which was set in
OL,21,F1976 in Southampton.
OL,26,@zD@AOUzD@TO]
