OL,3,CThousands gather for summer solstice
OL,4,Cas UK braces for sweltering heatwave
OL,6,FOn Sunday morning, a crowd of more
OL,7,Fthan 20,000 people flocked to
OL,8,FStonehenge and Avebury in Wiltshire to
OL,9,Fsee the sun rise at 4.25 am on the
OL,10,Flongest day of the year, according to
OL,11,FEnglish Heritage.
OL,13,FVisitors, some wearing flower head-
OL,14,Fdresses, touched the ancient monument
OL,15,Fand cheered as the glowing sun peeked
OL,16,Fover the misty horizon.
OL,18,FMeanwhile, Europe is also sweltering
OL,19,Funder the heatwave, with temperatures
OL,20,Fforecast to hit 37C in Rome and 39C in
OL,21,FMadrid on Monday.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/9
