OL,3,CThousands gather for summer solstice
OL,4,Cas UK braces for sweltering heatwave
OL,6,FIn France, highs of 40C are expected
OL,7,Fon Sunday, with Monday likely to be
OL,8,Feven hotter as emergency services and
OL,9,Fmilitary forces have been put on
OL,10,Fwildfire alert.
OL,12,FPublic alcohol consumption
OL,13,Frestrictions have also been put in
OL,14,Fplace by French authorities, and some
OL,15,Foutdoor sporting events have been
OL,16,Fcancelled.
OL,18,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,19,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,20,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,21,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/9
