OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1782082983
OL,3,CThousands gather for summer solstice
OL,4,Cas UK braces for sweltering heatwave
OL,6,FIn the UK, Sunday is expected to be a
OL,7,F"fine, bright day" and dry for most
OL,8,Fexcept for potential showers in north-
OL,9,Feast England, Met Office meteorologist
OL,10,FJonathan Vautrey said in an online
OL,11,Fforecast.
OL,13,FHighs of 31C are forecast in London
OL,14,Falong with 27C in Cardiff and 21C in
OL,15,FScotland and Northern Ireland.
OL,17,FMonday will be a "cloudier day
OL,18,Foverall", with temperatures expected
OL,19,Fto reach up to 32C with humidity
OL,20,Fforecast to rise throughout the week,
OL,21,Fhe said.
OL,26,@oD@AOUoD@RO]yD@ROUzD@HO]
