PN,31405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1782082983
OL,3,CThousands gather for summer solstice
OL,4,Cas UK braces for sweltering heatwave
OL,6,F"It's particularly across central
OL,7,Fsouthern regions, where we have an
OL,8,Fextreme heat warning, an amber extreme
OL,9,Fheat warning issued, where we could
OL,10,Fsee quite widely amongst the
OL,11,Fpopulation some heat-related impacts
OL,12,Fthroughout the week," Mr Vautrey said.
OL,14,F"Temperatures climbing towards the mid-
OL,15,F30s in places, that is quite
OL,16,Fexceptional for June."
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@UO]vD@AOUxD@VO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/9
