PN,31406
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1782082983
OL,3,CThousands gather for summer solstice
OL,4,Cas UK braces for sweltering heatwave
OL,6,FAn amber extreme heat warning has been
OL,7,Fissued by the weather service for
OL,8,FMonday and Tuesday for most of
OL,9,Fsouthern England, south-eastern and
OL,10,Feastern Wales, and much of the
OL,11,FMidlands.
OL,13,FThe alert flags potential health
OL,14,Fimpacts for people vulnerable to
OL,15,Fextreme heat and heat-related issues
OL,16,Ffor the wider population, as well as a
OL,17,Fpotential increase in water safety
OL,18,Fincidents.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,315,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31407
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1782082983
OL,3,CThousands gather for summer solstice
OL,4,Cas UK braces for sweltering heatwave
OL,6,FPeople in the alert area are advised
OL,7,Fto drink plenty of fluids and to keep
OL,8,Fout of the sun, and avoid exercising
OL,9,Fbetween 11am and 3pm, the Met Office
OL,10,Fsaid.
OL,12,FSeparate amber heat health alerts have
OL,13,Fbeen issued by the UK Health Security
OL,14,FAgency (UKHSA) for the east, south-
OL,15,Feast and south-west of England from
OL,16,FMonday morning until Wednesday evening.
OL,18,FA UKHSA yellow heat alert is also in
OL,19,Fplace for Yorkshire and Humber, north-
OL,20,Feast and north-west England during the
OL,21,Fsame period.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,315,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31408
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1782082983
OL,3,CThousands gather for summer solstice
OL,4,Cas UK braces for sweltering heatwave
OL,6,F"I'm sure many of us will be wanting
OL,7,Fto get outside and enjoying some of
OL,8,Fthis heat, but it certainly is worth
OL,9,Ftaking care as we could see some
OL,10,Fimpacts around," Mr Vautrey added.
OL,12,F"Water safety as well is going to be
OL,13,Fparamount if you are by the coast or
OL,14,Fother water bodies in land as well,
OL,15,Fand do follow the safety advice of
OL,16,Frelative authorities in order to avoid
OL,17,Fthe cold water shock when you are
OL,18,Fheading into any water areas."
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@PO]tD@AOUzD@^O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/9
