FL,315,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31409
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1782082983
OL,3,CThousands gather for summer solstice
OL,4,Cas UK braces for sweltering heatwave
OL,6,FThe heat comes after at least 15
OL,7,Fpeople died after getting into trouble
OL,8,Fin open water during a hot spell in
OL,9,FMay.
OL,11,FSamantha Hughes, national water safety
OL,12,Fpartner at the Royal National Lifeboat
OL,13,FInstitution, said: "With warmer
OL,14,Fweather approaching, it's important to
OL,15,Fremember that the water is still cold.
OL,17,F"Entering it unexpectedly can lead to
OL,18,Fcold water shock, causing a sudden
OL,19,Fincrease in breathing and heart rate,
OL,20,Fwhich may trigger panic."
OL,26,@uD@TOUyD@AOU|D@YO]
